snippet.title: MY HERO ULTRA RUMBLE - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready to go PLUS ULTRA as your favorite Hero or cause ultimate chaos as your favorite Villain?

It’s all possible in MY HERO ULTRA RUMBLE – a 24 player Battle Royale set in the MY HERO ACADEMIA Universe!

Pre-Register for the Closed Beta now: https://bnent.eu/MHUR_CBT

Follow us on:
Web: https://www.bandainamcoent.eu
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bandainamcoeu
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Bandainamcoeu 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bandainamcoeu

#MyHeroUltraRumble #MHA
